name: Online Tutor For English
overview:
US native English tutors tutor for English, SAT-English, writing and TOEFL with customize budget options and online tutorials; online learning materials for writing and spoken English, grammar, video lessons and quizzes.

Our students speak English either as a Second Language (ESL) or they are native speakers that need to advance their English language skills as junior-high and high school students, college students and adults from different walks of life. Teachers and students meet in the Skype Conferencing Room enhanced with multimedia tools, such as smart board, microphone and headphone, video, document sharing, discussion rooms, email, and free Live-Chat help, for one-to-one tutoring.

We offer Online English Language Courses for those who need a fast-paced course to improve their English language knowledge for spoken or written English, under the supervision of an English language tutor.

As to our low-cost but highly effective online English teaching program, we offer online English Language Tutorials, for all budgets, to help our clients advance their spoken English and writing. These tutorials are targeted to native English and non-native English speakers from different walks of life, and written for three different levels: beginner, intermediate and advanced. Access to the tutorials is three months plus help 24/7 through email.
